org.apache.flex.compiler.filespecs

Class CombinedFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.filespecs.CombinedFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFileSpecification

    public class CombinedFile
extends Object
implements IFileSpecification
    This is an IFileSpecification that include multiple source files into one. JFlex-generated tokenizers can skip BOM at the beginning of a file, but not elsewhere. This class skips BOM header in each source file so that the merged file won't have a BOM in the middle of a file.
